 ab-initio lasing theory 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "tureci_self-consistent_2006,tureci_strong_2008,tureci_ab_2009,ge_quantitative_2008,ge_steady-state_2010"

\end_inset

