\begin_inset Formula $\mathsf{A}_{0}\mathsf{v}_{k}=0$
\end_inset

.
 There are also left eigenvectors 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "strang_linear_algebra"

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathsf{w}_{j}$
\end_inset

