reference "eq:final linear eigenvalue problem"

\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula $2|a|^{2}\times$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\left(\begin{array}{cccc}
\Im\left(\frac{I}{H}\right) & \pm\Im\left(\frac{I+J+K}{H}\right) & -\Re\left(\frac{K}{H}\right) & \pm\Re\left(\frac{K}{H}\right)\\
